  <p class="gd-byline" style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:12.5px;letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(--blue-soft);opacity:.9;margin:16px 0 0">By <a href="/about" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px">Vegard Knudsen</a> · Founder, Heliski Travel · Updated 8 May 2026</p>
  <p class="gd-lede">Georgia has become the go-to name for skiers chasing big-mountain heli terrain on a budget, with the vast Greater Caucasus offering serious altitude for a fraction of Alpine prices. This honest guide weighs the value against the trade-offs, before pointing you towards our <a href="/packages">packages</a> and the more polished alternative of <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
